随着 6 音乐收视率飙升，弗农·凯 (Vernon Kay) 失去了肯·布鲁斯 (Ken Bruce) 的 BBC 广播 2 台 130 万听众https://www.nme.com/news/music/vernon-kay-loses-1-3million-of-ken-bruce-bbc-radio-2-listeners-6-music- ratings-soar-3522209?utm_source= rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=vernon-kay-loses-1-3million-of-ken-bruce-bbc-radio-2-listeners-6-music- ratings-soarTom Skinner Thu, 26 Oct 2023 14:35:34 +0000 Music NewsNewsBBC https://www.nme.com/?p=3522209 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/VernonKay-Radio-2-listening-figures-Rajar.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="弗农·凯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/VernonKay-Radio-2-listening-figures-Rajar.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/VernonKay-Radio-2-listening-figures-Rajar-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/VernonKay-Radio-2-listening-figures-Rajar-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/VernonKay-Radio-2-listening-figures-Rajar-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/VernonKay-Radio-2-listening-figures-Rajar-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/VernonKay-Radio-2-listening-figures-Rajar-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Rajar 发布了 2023 年最新收听数据</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/vernon-kay-loses-1-3million-of-ken-bruce-bbc-radio-2-listeners-6-music-ratings-soar-3522209">随着 6 音乐收视率飙升，弗农·凯 (Vernon Kay) 失去了肯·布鲁斯 (Ken Bruce) 的 BBC 广播 2 台 130 万听众，这一消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/VernonKay-Radio-2-listening-figures-Rajar.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="弗农·凯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/VernonKay-Radio-2-listening-figures-Rajar.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/VernonKay-Radio-2-listening-figures-Rajar-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/VernonKay-Radio-2-listening-figures-Rajar-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/VernonKay-Radio-2-listening-figures-Rajar-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/VernonKay-Radio-2-listening-figures-Rajar-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/VernonKay-Radio-2-listening-figures-Rajar-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>弗农·凯 (Vernon Kay) 在 BBC Radio 2 上的节目的听众数量比他的前任肯·布鲁斯 (Ken Bruce) 时少了 130 万，而 6 Music 的收视率继续飙升。</p><p> Bruce 是 Radio 2 任职时间最长的 DJ 之一， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ken-bruce-on-the-fate-on-popmaster-after-quitting-bbc-radio-2-show-3383638">他于 3 月份离开电台</a>，并于下个月加入 Greatest Hits Radio。此后，凯永久取代了他的上午节目。</p><p>广播行业机构<a href="https://www.rajar.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Rajar</em></a>分享的新数据显示，Kay 目前吸引了 690 万听众，比 Bruce 在 Radio 2 上的听众少了 130 万（来自<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-67220290" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>BBC 新闻</em></a>）。</p><p>但这些数字确实意味着凯拥有英国最受欢迎的广播节目。</p><p> <em>Rajar</em>的最新观众数据每年发布四次，时间跨度为 2023 年 6 月至 9 月。这是首次涵盖 Kay 整整三个月的观众数据，Kay 在 5 月举办了他的首场演出。</p><p> BBC 首席内容官夏洛特·摩尔 (Charlotte Moore) 表示：“Radio 2 仍然是英国最受欢迎的电台，我很高兴弗农·凯 (Vernon Kay) 在上午中旬成为英国最大的广播节目，带来了他的温暖和活力。以及对全国各地听众的魅力。” </p><div class="ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0" data-component="text-block"><div class="ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1"><p> Radio 2 的控制员海伦·托马斯 (Helen Thomas) 补充说，她“为 Radio 2 仍然是英国收听率最高的广播电台感到自豪”。</p><p>该电台每周有 1350 万听众，比 2022 年同期减少了 100 万。</p><p>根据<em>拉贾尔的说法</em>，布鲁斯<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ken-bruce-on-the-fate-on-popmaster-after-quitting-bbc-radio-2-show-3383638">在 Greatest Hits Radio 上进行了他深受喜爱的 PopMaster 测验</a>，他的新节目的观众人数已增加到 370 万。</p><p>在之前的更新中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bbc-radio-2-loses-a-million-listeners-since-ken-bruce-departure-3477772">收视机构发现，布鲁斯退出后，第二台广播失去了 100 万听众</a>。</p><p>与此同时， <em>Rajar</em>的最新观众数据显示，BBC 6 Music（纯数字另类电台）每周的观众人数为 280 万（来自<em><a href="https://www.musicweek.com/media/read/rajar-q3-analysis-bbc-radio-6-music-ratings-soar-following-schedule-changes/088722" target="_blank" rel="noopener">音乐周</a></em>）。这一数字同比增长11.7%，环比增长3.1%。</p><p> 6 Music remains the biggest digital radio station, and is home to shows hosted by the likes of Lauren Laverne, Huey Morgan and <a href="/artists/elbow">Elbow</a> &#39;s Guy Garvey. Laverne&#39;s breakfast programme currently has 1.4million listeners.</p><p> In May 2022, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bbc-6-music-posts-record-listening-figures-20th-year-3229539">6 Music posted record listening figures in the first quarter of its 20th year of operation</a> .</p></div></div><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/vernon-kay-loses-1-3million-of-ken-bruce-bbc-radio-2-listeners-6-music-ratings-soar-3522209">Vernon Kay loses 1.3million of Ken Bruce&#39;s BBC Radio 2 listeners as 6 Music ratings soar</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
